Announcing the release of Perl Module Math::Polynomial Version 0.03

Math::Polynomial  - Algebra on polynomials

This package provides operators to preform algebra on polynomials. The
operators +,-,*,/, and % are all implemented, as are evaluation of
polynomials. In addition, the package provides polynom interpolation
using Lagrange's formula, given a set of data points.

